data.description: Don't miss your chance to view this adorable home on Townsend Way just outside Fairbanks for the perfect Alaskan secluded feel! From the minute you drive up to the property you are welcomed by the acre of land surrounded by nature to give you that piece of privacy and a large front deck perfect for entertaining on these long summer days. Walking inside you are greeted by the mud room that lead past the gorgeous wood panel storage closets on the way to your kitchen and open living room. Talking about storage, your wall length cabinet in the living room and coffee/bar area provides a ton of extra storage. And as if the home couldn't get any better, you have a wood stove for a perfect secondary source of heat to keep you nice and toasty on those blistering winter nights. If you want the real alaskan feel with the opportunity to put your own personal touch on a perfect starter home, this is it. Don't miss your chance to view this adorable property and make it yours!
